## Directory Tree (agent-context/)

```
agent-context/
├── AGENT_INDEX.md              <- this file
├── business-context.md         <- product, parent platform, this app's role
├── architecture.md             <- routing, lazy-loading, feature decomposition
├── conventions.md              <- naming, hooks order, path aliases, file org
├── design-system.md            <- tokens, typography, spacing, RTL
├── ui-components.md            <- component library usage, wrappers
├── state-management.md         <- contexts, hooks, query patterns
├── error-handling.md           <- ErrorBoundary, API errors, 5xx handling
├── i18n.md                     <- locales, RTL mechanics  (omit if no i18n)
├── testing.md                  <- test types, framework setup, mocking rules
├── infrastructure.md           <- build (Vite/Next/etc.), env vars, deploy
├── glossary.md                 <- domain terminology
├── api-clients/                <- one file per backend service consumed
│   └── {service}.md            <- e.g., publisher.md, backoffice.md
└── features/                   <- one file per UI feature module
    └── {feature}.md            <- e.g., auth.md, publisher-dashboard.md
```

